basics.summary: Highly skilled and detail-oriented Software Engineer with 1.5 years of experience in developing, testing, and maintaining software applications. Proficient in a wide range of programming languages including Java, Python, C++, and JavaScript, with a strong background in algorithms, data structures, and software design patterns. Adept at collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions on time and within budget. Demonstrated expertise in full software development lifecycle (SDLC) including requirements analysis, design, implementation, testing, and deployment. Passionate about learning new technologies and continuously improving technical skills.
